<h2>Wall Studs Model</h2>
<p>
    Using world tracking and model placement produced a less convincing result for the 3D Wall Studs model than for the 3D
    Floorplan model. Using the ground floor as reference, the 3D model was placed in the world space according to the pivot 
    point attached to bottom of the SceneKit model. As demonstrated, the model follows a vanishing point not aligned with 
    the wall in the world space. Image tracking would be a promising solution for this model, as the model has minimal depth
    and would stick well to a flat plane.
</p>
